  U.S. Department of Commerce NTIA/ITS
  Institute for Telecommunication Sciences
  TA Services Account Application Form
     __________________________________________________________________

   All users of TA Services MUST agree to one of the following CRADAs:
     * Fee-for-Use CRADA - User access to previously developed models and
       methods on a fee-for-use basis and is available 24 hours a day, 7
       days a week throughout the year.
     * Software Development CRADA - Software development of new or
       improved models that would ultimately be available in the regular
       suite of TA Services.

   It is a legally binding agreement between you and NTIA/ITS.
   Note: TA Services is a Pay-per-use service. A minumum deposit of $500
   is required to open a new account.
   Note: The above CRADAs apply only to U.S. based companies. TA Services
   is not authorized to accept funds from foreign companies.
